data.description: KB Ironwood subdivision. Plan 3 This well located single story has upgrades. Four bedrooms and two bathrooms. From the entryway there is vinyl  wood plank flooring leading into the great room with high ceilings, LED lighting with over head fan and lots of window light. The great room is open to the kitchen and dining areas making it nice for entertaining. The kitchen has dark colored cabinetry, sandstone colored granite countertops, stainless appliances and huge island bar area. This separated floor plan has private primary bedroom and bathroom on its on wing. The bathroom includes a separated tub - shower, raised cabinets and walk in closet space . The secondary bedrooms share a full bathroom. There are wooden blinds through out the home, 10' raised panel doors and over head lighting with fans in each bedroom. Indoor laundry room with extra cabinets. Tankless water heater, fire sprinkler system. The garage is finished drywalled and has epoxy painted flooring. The rear yard has a covered patio, concrete walk ways and landscaped yard ready to enjoy. There is a solar system to  lowers your electric utility bill. (Lowest mo. bill was $14.94c & Highest monthly bill was $73.68c). Well maintained and move in ready home located in desirable subdivision with new homes being built.
